# Markdown wiki conventions

## Required YAML frontmatter (knowledge pages)

```yaml
---
title: Page Title
category: concept|entity|reference|project|node|skill|meta|doc
tags: [tag1, tag2]
summary: One line for RAG-lite scan
created: YYYY-MM-DD
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
---
```

Nodes may include `triggers: [keyword1, keyword2]`.

## Linking

Use Obsidian-style `[[wikilinks]]` or `[[path/to/page|display text]]`.

## RAG-lite query order

1. Scan `summary` and `title` in frontmatter via search
2. Open only matching `.md` bodies
3. Cite paths in answers

## After ingest

Update `index.md`, `.manifest.json`, `log.md`, `hot.md`.
